    public static enum BlockImageIcon.ImageLocation
extends java.lang.Enum<BlockImageIcon.ImageLocation>
    ImageLocation specifies the relative location of this BlockImageIcon within the visible Block instance of this BlockGenus. Note: there is only one BlockImageIcon per ImageLocation within a Block
